00:29:37,173 --> 00:29:40,816
earlier, they'll use specific props and messages in their

486
00:29:40,836 --> 00:29:44,759
levels. They'll repeat props. You know, Zelda has the very

487
00:29:44,799 --> 00:29:48,782
classic like broken rock that says, hey, this can be, a bomb

