00:32:53,118 --> 00:32:54,319
the facing screen left.

535
00:32:55,319 --> 00:32:57,179
So you can actually see the X. We actually hide it from the

536
00:32:57,199 --> 00:32:59,480
player completely with our cameras to make sure that

537
00:32:59,600 --> 00:33:01,721
they're more enticed, more willing to click

538
00:33:01,801 --> 00:33:02,481
on the broken glass.

539
00:33:05,101 --> 00:33:11,685
So when they do, we actually played a cinematic and that revealed the X.

