00:33:53,498 --> 00:33:57,359
And so we're always pushing the player, hey, make a connection between these two things

554
00:33:57,399 --> 00:33:59,880
because there's a narrative there and it's part of the puzzle.

555
00:34:04,343 --> 00:34:08,307
If you don't highlight what you want your player to click on,

556
00:34:08,888 --> 00:34:13,673
you get something like this, which is a very classic adventure game pitfall

