00:39:17,203 --> 00:39:17,803
out what's happening.

651
00:39:17,823 --> 00:39:21,726
It's time for me to sit and think and look at the scene and understand what's happening

652
00:39:21,766 --> 00:39:21,887
here.

653
00:39:21,907 --> 00:39:29,093
Another important thing to remember when building a puzzle is to be kind.

654
00:39:29,513 --> 00:39:30,754
Just be kind to your player.

655
00:39:32,846 --> 00:39:36,332
It's a contract of challenging them, but then not making things impossible.

656
00:39:38,435 --> 00:39:39,517
Repetition isn't fun.

